      "content": "i guess... it just feels like a lot of work. trying to build something, trying to love people, trying to make a life when you know it's all just going to be swallowed up by entropy anyway. it feels like fighting a tide that's already won. why even bother putting in the effort to keep going when the outcome is always just... nothingness?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
